{"snp2.2:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.2 ","snp2.2:0.2":"Amagandhasutta ","snp2.2:1.1":"“Samakacingulakacinakani ca, ","snp2.2:1.2":"Pattapphalam mulaphalam gavipphalam; ","snp2.2:1.3":"Dhammena laddham satamasnamana, ","snp2.2:1.4":"Na kamakama alikam bhananti. ","snp2.2:2.1":"Yadasnamano sukatam sunitthitam, ","snp2.2:2.2":"Parehi dinnam payatam panitam; ","snp2.2:2.3":"Salinamannam paribhunjamano, ","snp2.2:2.4":"So bhunjasi kassapa amagandham. ","snp2.2:3.1":"Na amagandho mama kappatiti, ","snp2.2:3.2":"Icceva tvam bhasasi brahmabandhu; ","snp2.2:3.3":"Salinamannam paribhunjamano, ","snp2.2:3.4":"Sakuntamamsehi susankhatehi; ","snp2.2:3.5":"Pucchami tam kassapa etamattham, ","snp2.2:3.6":"Kathampakaro tava amagandho”. ","snp2.2:4.1":"“Panatipato vadhachedabandhanam, ","snp2.2:4.2":"Theyyam musavado nikativancanani ca; ","snp2.2:4.3":"Ajjhenakuttam paradarasevana, ","snp2.2:4.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:5.1":"Ye idha kamesu asannata jana, ","snp2.2:5.2":"Rasesu giddha asucibhavamassita; ","snp2.2:5.3":"Natthikaditthi visama durannaya, ","snp2.2:5.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:6.1":"Ye lukhasa daruna pitthimamsika, ","snp2.2:6.2":"Mittadduno nikkarunatimanino; ","snp2.2:6.3":"Adanasila na ca denti kassaci, ","snp2.2:6.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:7.1":"Kodho mado thambho paccupatthapana, ","snp2.2:7.2":"Maya usuya bhassasamussayo ca; ","snp2.2:7.3":"Manatimano ca asabbhi santhavo, ","snp2.2:7.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:8.1":"Ye papasila inaghatasucaka, ","snp2.2:8.2":"Voharakuta idha patirupika; ","snp2.2:8.3":"Naradhama yedha karonti kibbisam, ","snp2.2:8.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:9.1":"Ye idha panesu asannata jana, ","snp2.2:9.2":"Paresamadaya vihesamuyyuta; ","snp2.2:9.3":"Dussilaludda pharusa anadara, ","snp2.2:9.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:10.1":"Etesu giddha viruddhatipatino, ","snp2.2:10.2":"Niccuyyuta pecca tamam vajanti ye; ","snp2.2:10.3":"Patanti satta nirayam avamsira, ","snp2.2:10.4":"Esamagandho na hi mamsabhojanam. ","snp2.2:11.1":"Na macchamamsanamanasakattam, ","snp2.2:11.2":"Na naggiyam na mundiyam jatajallam; ","snp2.2:11.3":"Kharajinani naggihuttassupasevana, ","snp2.2:11.4":"Ye vapi loke amara bahu tapa; ","snp2.2:11.5":"Mantahuti yannamutupasevana, ","snp2.2:11.6":"Sodhenti maccam avitinnakankham. ","snp2.2:12.1":"Sotesu gutto viditindriyo care, ","snp2.2:12.2":"Dhamme thito ajjavamaddave rato; ","snp2.2:12.3":"Sangatigo sabbadukkhappahino, ","snp2.2:12.4":"Na lippati ditthasutesu dhiro”. ","snp2.2:13.1":"Iccetamattham bhagava punappunam, ","snp2.2:13.2":"Akkhasi nam vedayi mantaparagu; ","snp2.2:13.3":"Citrahi gathahi muni pakasayi, ","snp2.2:13.4":"Niramagandho asito durannayo. ","snp2.2:14.1":"Sutvana buddhassa subhasitam padam, ","snp2.2:14.2":"Niramagandham sabbadukkhappanudanam; ","snp2.2:14.3":"Nicamano vandi tathagatassa, ","snp2.2:14.4":"Tattheva pabbajjamarocayitthati. ","snp2.2:14.5":"Amagandhasuttam dutiyam. "}